title: Florence Zeitingale 4/1: Florida, Zantac, Zoom, Tekashi69
itunes:title: Florence Zeitingale 4/1: Florida, Zantac, Zoom, Tekashi69
description:
On this edition of Florence Zeitingale Jack and Miles discuss Florida finally enacting a Stay at Home order, the FDA has ordered that Zantac be pulled from shelves, the rise of Zoom has lead to a rise in scrutiny of some of Zoom's actual policies and practices, and Tekashi69 wants to get out of prison early.
